      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition car that runs and drives well and has clearly been cared for. It shows normal wear for its age and use, with some cosmetic blemishes you\u2019d expect on a used vehicle, but overall it presents well and should make a solid daily driver. Everything important feels sound, and buyers can expect a dependable vehicle with the usual routine maintenance of any used car, not a perfect showpiece.",
