    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "An affordable, straightforward vehicle that offers dependable transportation for the budget-conscious buyer. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it presents a practical opportunity for someone seeking low-cost motoring, a starter vehicle, or a project with potential. Priced to reflect condition while delivering strong value, it\u2019s a smart buy for anyone who appreciates honest offerings and room to make it their own.",
