      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it starts, moves, and could make a great cheap runaround, project, or parts donor depending on what you need. If you\u2019re handy with cars or just after something inexpensive to get you by, this could be a solid little opportunity. Priced to sell and offered honestly.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid old-school driver with a tough-running powertrain and plenty of character. Starts up, moves out, and offers a great foundation for someone who wants an affordable daily, weekend cruiser, or light project. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission does its job, and the chassis still feels honest and usable. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. If you want a cheap, straightforward car with good bones and room to make it your own, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
