      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of road presence that turns heads and sparks imagination. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates honest character and sees the appeal in bringing a well-traveled machine back into the spotlight. Whether you\u2019re after an affordable project, a dependable backup with soul, or something to tinker with on weekends, this one offers charm, potential, and a story waiting for its next chapter.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking low-cost transportation or a solid project opportunity. It offers strong value for the money, with plenty of usable life for the right owner and an easy entry point into ownership without a major investment. A smart buy for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly deal.",
      "price": 4495.0,
